excerpt: Previously rumored to be dating Kendall Jenner, here's why Phoenix Suns guard Devin Booker recently sparked dating rumors with Molly Murphy.
siteName: ComingSoon.net - Movie Trailers, TV & Streaming News, and More
text: Fans speculate that the Phoenix Suns guard Devin Booker is dating Molly Murphy, who accompanied him at the Stagecoach music festival. The 28-year-old NBA standout, who previously dated Kendall Jenner, was spotted in an embrace with the social media star at the event, fueling rumors about a potential new romantic connection. So, here are all the details of the dating rumors surrounding Booker and Murphy, as well as the truth behind them. Is Devin Booker dating Molly Murphy? Fans spotted Devin Booker and Molly Murphy in a close embrace at the Stagecoach music festival on April 27, 2025. However, neither has confirmed their relationship as of writing. As per an Instagram post shared by Deauxmoi, the three-time NBA All-Star reportedly used a private back area of the venue as their entry and exit. In the photographs, Booker was lightly wrapping his arms around Murphy while walking. Later, she posted a picture of her Stagecoach fit on her Instagram story, which convinced fans that it was she who was spotted with the NBA star. Check out the rumored pair’s photos below: Previously, David Booker was reportedly in a relationship with Kendall Jenner. The duo sparked dating rumors from 2020 onwards. As per People, the basketball player almost made it “official” in January 2021 when he reposted a bikini-clad Jenner’s picture on his Instagram story, captioning it “whew.” Neither of the two clarified anything publicly at the time. However, a source told the outlet, “Kendall and Devin have spent the past few weeks together. They have mostly enjoyed Malibu, but over the weekend, they were vacationing with Justin and Hailey in Idaho.” The source added, “They were all enjoying the lake life and also played golf.” A month later, Jenner and Booker debuted their relationship to their massive Instagram following on Valentine’s Day. (via People) Albeit almost a year later, reports stated that the supermodel had broken up with the budding NBA star. After a breakup and even a reunion, Kendall Jenner and Devin Booker finally called it quits in 2022. The two parted ways due to busy schedules, according to another report by People. During Valentine’s weekend 2025, E! News reported that the former pair were again spotted having dinner together in Aspen. However, neither of the two confirmed any rumors of reconciliation. Meanwhile, Devin Booker and his currently rumored partner, Molly Murphy, have yet to comment on their dating rumors.
html:
Fans speculate that the Phoenix Suns guard Devin Booker is dating Molly Murphy, who accompanied him at the Stagecoach music festival. The 28-year-old NBA standout, who previously dated Kendall Jenner, was spotted in an embrace with the social media star at the event, fueling rumors about a potential new romantic connection.

So, here are all the details of the dating rumors surrounding Booker and Murphy, as well as the truth behind them.

Is Devin Booker dating Molly Murphy?

Fans spotted Devin Booker and Molly Murphy in a close embrace at the Stagecoach music festival on April 27, 2025. However, neither has confirmed their relationship as of writing.

As per an Instagram post shared by Deauxmoi, the three-time NBA All-Star reportedly used a private back area of the venue as their entry and exit. In the photographs, Booker was lightly wrapping his arms around Murphy while walking. Later, she posted a picture of her Stagecoach fit on her Instagram story, which convinced fans that it was she who was spotted with the NBA star.

Check out the rumored pair’s photos below:

Previously, David Booker was reportedly in a relationship with Kendall Jenner. The duo sparked dating rumors from 2020 onwards. As per People, the basketball player almost made it “official” in January 2021 when he reposted a bikini-clad Jenner’s picture on his Instagram story, captioning it “whew.”

Neither of the two clarified anything publicly at the time. However, a source told the outlet, “Kendall and Devin have spent the past few weeks together. They have mostly enjoyed Malibu, but over the weekend, they were vacationing with Justin and Hailey in Idaho.” The source added, “They were all enjoying the lake life and also played golf.”

A month later, Jenner and Booker debuted their relationship to their massive Instagram following on Valentine’s Day. (via People) Albeit almost a year later, reports stated that the supermodel had broken up with the budding NBA star. After a breakup and even a reunion, Kendall Jenner and Devin Booker finally called it quits in 2022. The two parted ways due to busy schedules, according to another report by People.

During Valentine’s weekend 2025, E! News reported that the former pair were again spotted having dinner together in Aspen. However, neither of the two confirmed any rumors of reconciliation.

Meanwhile, Devin Booker and his currently rumored partner, Molly Murphy, have yet to comment on their dating rumors.
